description: Regenerate route catalog and OpenAPI metadata when only routes change.
globs: src/domains/**/*.routes.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

## Route catalog sync

When any `*.routes.ts` file is created or modified:

1. Read `.cursor/skills/route-catalog/SKILL.md` and run `pnpm routes:catalog` once.
2. Read `.cursor/skills/openapi-route-sync/SKILL.md` — add or update `schema: { summary, description, tags }` on each Fastify route registration plus locale tags; run `pnpm docs:generate:multilang` when operation text changed.
3. If routes affect seeds, run **seed-maintainer** per skill-index.

CI enforces drift via `pnpm routes:catalog:check`.
